This is a great Anna Nicole Smith Collection! Sure, nothing beats her Playboy DVD's especially "The Complete Anna Nicole Smith DVD", but this is still awesome! This includes two of Anna's action movies, "To The Limit", and "Skyscraper", "Skyscraper" is definetly the better of the two movies, but "To The Limit" is also good. Anna Nicole has much more screen time in "Skyscraper" than she does in "To The Limit". "Anna Nicole Exposed" is the 3rd dvd is the set, and definetly the best! This dvd is very sexy, and Anna Nicole reveals all of her sexiest fantasies! Very erotic! This is a must-have for every Anna Nicole fan!!! Also don't for get about Anna's new special on E! on June 20th, also don't forget that Anna will be in the movie "Be Cool", the sequal to "Get Shorty"!
